    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">真夏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まなつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">午</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひる</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">片日向</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かたひなた</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
苔すこし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">泥</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひぢ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ばみ青む<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">捨石</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">すていし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳩酢草</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はとかたばみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">呼吸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">細</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほそ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>う<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">雫</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しずく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">湿</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うる</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ひ<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">実</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">み</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">持</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">も</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ちぬ、かつ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">喘息</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あへ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぎつゝ。<lb />
<lb />
そのかみ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">誰</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">た</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">小</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ちひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さなる<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">性</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さが</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">得</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">え</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>て、また<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">誰</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なれ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">恋</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ひて、その<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">熟実</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うみみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
かつこぼし、かつ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夜</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">待</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ちて、<lb />
いづ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">方</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かた</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>へ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">精進</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さうじ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">魂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぞ。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳩酢草</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はとかたばみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はえも知らず、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">捨石</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">すていし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に。――<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">小雨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こさめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のあとの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">風</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かぜ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いきれ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">木々</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きゞ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>みな<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">死</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">し</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぬと<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">泣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">庭</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">には</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、ひとり<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">静</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しづか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
おほどかに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夢</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に入るさま。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">蚊帳</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かや</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">繞</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">めぐ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">名香</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みやうかう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">手枕</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たまくら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">頬</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>もひた<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">痩</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">や</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>せて病める身の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">予</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">横臥</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よこふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しぬ。心こそ、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳩酢草</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はとかたばみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">魂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たましひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にさながら似たれ。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">風</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かぜ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>また<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">薫</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くゆ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>り<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">小雨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こさめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しぬ。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳩酢草</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はとかたばみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">予</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">一日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひとひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">天地</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あめつち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">幸福</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さいはひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ありき。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
